#: ../../../tools/rtla/rtla.rst:16
msgid ""
"The **rtla** is a meta-tool that includes a set of commands that aims to "
"analyze the real-time properties of Linux. But instead of testing Linux as a "
"black box, **rtla** leverages kernel tracing capabilities to provide precise "
"information about the properties and root causes of unexpected results."
msgstr ""

